Debile!

327
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:06,250
Hej, tady ne.

328
00:36:06,250 --> 00:36:07,980
Jdeme ven.

329
00:36:09,590 --> 00:36:11,170
Pojďte.

330
00:36:13,260 --> 00:36:14,310


331
